title: Psychology Laboratory Topics
description: Selected laboratory topics in the field of psychology. May be taken for credit two times as topics vary. Open to the following majors only: PC26, PC28, PC29, PC30, PC31, PC32, PC33, PC34, CG32. Prerequisites: upper-division standing, department approval, and PSYC 60 or COGS 14B and PSYC 70 or COGS 14A.
